data.description: Welcome to your dream home located at 6307 Landover Blvd in the beautiful city of Spring Hill, Florida. This stunning property boasts 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and a spacious 2880 living square feet, providing ample space for you and your family to live and grow. As you pull up to the property, you will be greeted by a 3-car attached garage, providing plenty of room for your vehicles and storage needs.Step inside and be amazed by the luxurious features this home has to offer. The kitchen is a chef's dream with granite countertops, modern appliances, and lots of cupboard space, perfect for preparing meals and entertaining guests. The Primary bedroom is large with en-suite bathroom. The additional bedrooms are generously sized and the bathrooms are equally as impressive with quartz countertops, adding a touch of elegance to your daily routine.But the beauty doesn't stop there. Step outside and be greeted by your very own outdoor kitchen, perfect for hosting summer barbeques and enjoying the Florida sunshine. The property is also fully fenced, providing privacy and security for you and your loved ones as you relax by the pool. With new double pane vinyl windows, you can enjoy the views while keeping your energy costs low.Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your forever home.
